code and excluding all of the fields on the first page, the form will now try to automatically load on the first page with fields.<\\/li>\\n<li>New: Added a new start_page option for the [editlink] shortcode to begin the form on a specific page.<\\/li>\\n<li>New: Added new <span class=\\\"blob-code-inner blob-code-marker\\\" data-code-marker=\\\"+\\\"><span class=\\\"pl-s\\\">frm_pro_field_has_variable_html_id, frm_pro_reports_boxes<\\/span><\\/span> filters, and <span class=\\\"blob-code-inner blob-code-marker\\\" data-code-marker=\\\"+\\\"><span class=\\\"pl-s\\\">frm_pro_after_field_report<\\/span><\\/span> hooks.<\\/li>\\n<li>New: Added new translations for Chinese, French, Spanish, Danish, and German.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Dynamic fields that use data from post actions were not importing properly.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Conditional dropdown fields with inside label positions were not displaying the labels as expected.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: [if x] shortcodes were sometimes not processing for very long forms.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\",\"plugin\":\"formidable-pro\\/formidable-pro.php\",\"icons\":{\"1x\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/icon-256x256.png\"},\"banners\":{\"high\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/banner-1544x500.png\",\"low\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/banner-772x250.png\"},\"search_terms\":\"\",\"beta\":{\"version\":\"5.0.06p\",\"plugin\":\"formidable\\/formidable.php\",\"package\":\"https:\\/\\/s3.amazonaws.com\\/fp.strategy11.com\\/releases\\/formidable-pro-5.0.06p.zip?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJ3QHAN4BJMSYZ3ZQ&Expires=1632895564&Signature=v3Rw4OGRRQTqRipefuWJHgJIBO0%3D\"},\"expires\":\"1654300799\",\"code\":\"valid\",\"date\":\"2018-11-28 19:20:00\",\"type\":\"elite\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/s3.amazonaws.com\\/fp.strategy11.com\\/releases\\/formidable-pro-5.0.06p.zip?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJ3QHAN4BJMSYZ3ZQ&Expires=1632895564&Signature=v3Rw4OGRRQTqRipefuWJHgJIBO0%3D\",\"timeout\":1632895564,\"package\":\"https:\\/\\/s3.amazonaws.c